      "author": "Stefan",
      "excerpt": "Our last stop was Calgary, where we only had one day to check things out. Unfortunately, we left feeling pretty let down. The city's design pushed us toward the long network of skywalks, which helped us get around but kept us mostly inside. This made it hard to really take in the vibe of the city since we missed out on the streets and sights we expected to see.",
